  Reduced the repository scope to unidirectional and directional third-order OW3D initialization generators.
- 2026-03-12
  Added `mf12_directional_generator.m` for MF12-based directional third-order wave-group initialization.
- 2026-03-12
  Updated the directional generator to use only local repository dependencies so it can be pushed to GitHub cleanly.
- 2026-03-12
  Added built-in visualization output for the linear directional wave group and the third-order MF12 result.
- 2026-03-12
  Added a plain-text backup of `Explanation_SettingsFile.rtf` as `Explanation_SettingsFile.txt`.
- 2026-03-12
  Reorganized generated-case roots to `uni initial condition/` and `directional initial condition/`.
- 2026-03-13
  Simplified the directional generator output logic back to normal surface-only OW3D output without kinematic-plane export.
- 2026-03-13
  Rebuilt the unidirectional generator to use the bundled MF12 interface directly and removed the older mixed Dalzell/VWA logic.
